### Why

Agent Teams parallel execution can cause file conflicts when multiple agents read/write the same file.
This lock manager maps Rust ownership semantics to file access: exclusive locks for writes, shared
locks for reads. Hooks intercept tool calls to transparently acquire/release locks via CLI subprocess.
